title: Rock A Bye Baby

description:
Description :
        I won't leave you who made me decide to live again.
Together even in hell, the guard dog × the chieftain's master-servant noir BL!
Year 20××.
The economy collapsed, and public order worsened.
Asahi, who was on the verge of ending his life in a dirty alley, is rescued by a young man who introduces himself as "Suzu".
Initially, Asahi, who intended to die, lashed out at Suzu, but since his true desire to live was exposed from the depths of his heart, he has come to forgive Suzu.
He may not be stable, but he doesn't seem deceitful either.
While treating him as if he were much younger, Suzu, who occasionally wears a surprisingly lonely expression, made Asahi's heart tremble for the first time.
That's what I thought.
I wanted to know more about Suzu.
No matter what kind of sorrow he carries—.
